  "text": "This technique modifies the structure of the program in form of physically reordering of the program codes, while preserving the execution order or flow of the program running using conditional jumps or unconditional branches. It may be done at the level of instructions or modules. Fig. 1 shows an example of such code structure modification used in Zperm virus [CITATION_1] .",
